<p>Here you will find a set of Sample Projects. Each one covers several different areas of functionality.  The scripts in these projects contain comments for you to read (that are ignored by Transcript) - look for the lines that start with a double dash -- and are colored purple.  There is also and Video and PDF that shows you how to use each one, in the Video Tutorials section (go back to the Learning Center to find this).</p>
<p></p>
<p>We recommend you have explored the introductory video tutorials so you have a basic understanding of how Dreamcard or Revolution work before you start on the Sample Projects.</p>